query:
SELECT
                session_id as "session_id!",
                COALESCE(user_type, 'unknown') as "user_type",
                started_at as "started_at!",
                duration_seconds,
                request_count,
                last_activity_at as "last_activity_at!"
            FROM user_sessions
            WHERE ended_at IS NULL
              AND last_activity_at >= $1
            ORDER BY last_activity_at DESC
            LIMIT $2
